videos.description: Auburn's Chuma Okeke comes up with a steal and throws down an easy two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Auburn's Okeke rises for 2-handed slam

videos.description: Auburn's Anfernee McLemore gets up for a nasty alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: McLemore throws down alley-oop slam

videos.description: Chris Silva muscles his way into the paint and throws down a wide-open one-handed slam.
videos.headline: South Carolina's Silva gets up for one-handed flush

videos.description: Keyshawn Bryant gets up over Auburn defenders for an emphatic tomahawk dunk.
videos.headline: Bryant skies for vicious tomahawk slam

videos.description: Chris Silva could not be stopped as he goes off for 30 points and 14 rebounds, leading the Gamecocks to an 80-77 win over No. 16 Auburn.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight ( Silva drops 30 to fuel South Carolina’s upset of Auburn) 2019/01/22 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Silva drops 30 to fuel South Carolina's upset of Auburn
